{"tid":1974903,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港之光]我想講香港本土藝人曾經都好勁，同日韓睇齊，上日本紅白","createTime":"2020-04-16T07:24:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T08:11:27.000Z","uid":146340,"like":3,"dislike":58,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"dd45f7c970d27d745ca0b46a70cef014aec89020","tid":1974903,"uid":146340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T07:24:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BHbKSjXoC3g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBHbKSjXoC3g&d=t1SY3LDExWMfWGGt1HQTgD2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=95dc63c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BHbKSjXoC3g</a><br />\n<br />\n無錯，就係譚詠麟，譚校長。<br />\n<br />\n從藝40多年來，譚詠麟創作的歌曲近百首，他作曲的歌曲多次獲得&ldquo;十大中文金曲獎&rdquo;、&ldquo;十大勁歌金曲獎&rdquo;、&ldquo;十大中文金曲最佳作曲獎&rdquo;等榮譽。2007年獲得CASH音樂成就大獎。2007至2009年擔任第八屆香港演藝人協會會長，同年獲香港特區政府頒授榮譽勛章，但因授獎典禮同時段正好是四川大地震後的慈善節目，寧願錯過授獎典禮也要去四川震後現場。2014年獲得IFPI香港流行音樂文化歌手大獎，以表彰他對香港音樂創作及華語樂壇的貢獻。同年亦入選十大中文金曲名人堂。<br />\n<br />\n譚詠麟在影壇曾於1981年憑著《假如我是真的》獲得金馬獎&ldquo;最佳劇情男主角&rdquo;。譚詠麟至今仍活躍樂壇。當被問及有關年齡問題時，他常自稱&ldquo;年年廿五歲&rdquo;，倡導健康、樂觀的人生觀。"},{"pid":"1575d6a31045ee34bcc8234062984976d74ac42a","tid":1974903,"uid":229026,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T07:26:16.000Z","msg":"有生之年想睇到廣東歌反攻世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c7d8ffd67405a369214aafe31a9e20c4a40a034","tid":1974903,"uid":6122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T07:26:57.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"742ec7e23a82847a1e5a825bd07a2a596c561b21","tid":1974903,"uid":301989,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T07:27:05.000Z","msg":"條死廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd492b037cace4938c645fd045d94e04aa2e642c","tid":1974903,"uid":52073,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T07:27:15.000Z","msg":"廢老譚不啦"},{"pid":"84da2e11f00be6a047802bc5fc4b75700835be5b","tid":19